---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
        title="About Luke | Full-Stack Developer with 10 Years Experience"
        description="Meet Luke, a seasoned full-stack developer with a decade of experience. Specializing in robust web applications, from backend architecture to frontend design."
>
    <div class="bg-yellow-100 py-8 sm:py-16 overflow-y-auto border-y-4 border-black min-h-[calc(100vh-264px)]">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <div class="bg-white border-4 border-black p-4 sm:p-8 shadow-[8px_8px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)] relative">
                <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-24 h-24 bg-blue-400 border-4 border-black transform rotate-12 translate-x-8 -translate-y-8"></div>
                <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-20 h-20 bg-pink-400 border-4 border-black rounded-full -translate-x-10 translate-y-10"></div>

                <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-black mb-8 transform -rotate-1 break-words relative z-10">
                    About Luke</h1>

                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 relative z-10">
                    <div class="bg-green-200 p-4 border-4 border-black shadow-[4px_4px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)] transform rotate-1">
                        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">The Developer</h2>
                        <p>Full-stack developer with almost 10 years of experience, specializing in crafting robust
                            web applications. Proficient in multiple programming languages and frameworks, with a
                            keen eye for both frontend design and backend architecture.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-blue-200 p-4 border-4 border-black shadow-[4px_4px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)] transform -rotate-1 md:col-span-2">
                        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">The Journey</h2>
                        <p>My journey in tech began with curiosity about how things work. Today, I tackle complex
                            problems with enthusiasm, turning them into elegant, efficient applications. I'm
                            committed to continuous learning and sharing knowledge.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-yellow-200 p-4 border-4 border-black shadow-[4px_4px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)] transform rotate-1 md:col-span-2">
                        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">The Approach</h2>
                        <p>As a seasoned developer, I've honed my skills in creating scalable, user-friendly
                            solutions that drive business growth. My expertise spans from backend architecture to
                            frontend design, ensuring seamless, end-to-end application development.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-purple-200 p-4 border-4 border-black shadow-[4px_4px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)] transform -rotate-1">
                        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">The Person</h2>
                        <p>Beyond coding, I'm a proud husband and father. Our family, complete with a cat and a dog,
                            keeps me grounded and inspired. We love exploring beautiful landscapes together. Whether
                            it's developing a cutting-edge application or spending quality time with my family, I
                            approach life with enthusiasm and dedication to excellence.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-pink-200 p-4 border-4 border-black shadow-[4px_4px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)] transform rotate-1 md:col-span-3">
                        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">The Geek</h2>
                        <p>In my free time, I embrace my inner geek. I'm an avid gamer, always ready for the next
                            big release or a nostalgic replay of classics. This passion often influences my approach
                            to creating engaging user experiences. I also enjoy tinkering with new technologies,
                            contributing to open-source projects, and attending tech meetups to stay connected with
                            the developer community.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    </div>
</Layout>